Multidisciplinary consensus on assessment of unruptured intracranial aneurysms: 
proposal of an international research group.

Etminan N(1), Beseoglu K, Barrow DL, Bederson J, Brown RD Jr, Connolly ES Jr, 
Derdeyn CP, Hänggi D, Hasan D, Juvela S, Kasuya H, Kirkpatrick PJ, Knuckey N, 
