of Helsinki, Helsinki, Finland (S.J.); Department of Neurosurgery, Tokyo Women's 
Medical University Medical Center East, Tokyo, Japan (H.K.); Neurosurgery Unit, 
Department of Clinical Neurosciences, Cambridge University Hospitals Trust, 
